OL,3,CPolice on alert as groups plan
OL,4,Cprotests over fuel prices across the UK
OL,6,FWords by James Hockaday
OL,8,FProtests over fuel prices are being
OL,9,Fplanned in London and other British
OL,10,Fcities, organisers have confirmed to
OL,11,FITV News, with several police forces
OL,12,Fon standby.
OL,14,FIt comes after slow-moving convoys of
OL,15,Ftractors and other vehicles brought
OL,16,Ftraffic to a standstill in parts of
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland on Tuesday, and even
OL,18,Fmore severe demonstrations in the
OL,19,FRepublic of Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776294181
OL,3,CPolice on alert as groups plan
OL,4,Cprotests over fuel prices across the UK
OL,6,FSpeculation has since been mounting
OL,7,Fover convoy protests in England and
OL,8,FScotland, with a poster titled
OL,9,F"England Fuel Protest" going viral on
OL,10,Fsocial media. It lists 14 locations
OL,11,Ffor protests planned on April 15, 16,
OL,12,Fand 17.
OL,14,FIt is not clear who made the poster,
OL,15,Fand reaction from police forces has
OL,16,Fbeen mixed, but campaign group
OL,17,FFairFuelUK said it is supporting
OL,18,Fprotests planned "in London and other
OL,19,Fcities".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776294181
OL,3,CPolice on alert as groups plan
OL,4,Cprotests over fuel prices across the UK
OL,6,F"Yes, fuel protests are being planned
OL,7,Fin London and other cities," the lobby
OL,8,Fgroup's founder Howard Cox told ITV
OL,9,FNews, adding, "details to be announced
OL,10,Fsoon."
OL,12,FCox, who stood as a Reform UK
OL,13,Fcandidate in the 2024 London mayoral
OL,14,Felection and joined far-right party
OL,15,FAdvance UK, said FairFuelUK "will
OL,16,Fcause minimal inconvenience to the
OL,17,Fpublic and businesses".
OL,19,FWhen asked, the politician and
OL,20,Fcampaigner did not say which other UK
OL,21,Fcities would be included.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776294181
OL,3,CPolice on alert as groups plan
OL,4,Cprotests over fuel prices across the UK
OL,6,FIn a press release on Monday, William
OL,7,FTaylor, coordinator of Farmers For
OL,8,FAction, said the protest group was
OL,9,F"privileged to be asked by farm
OL,10,Forganisations across the UK" to
OL,11,Fconsider a "UK-wide tax and fuel
OL,12,Fprotest".
OL,14,FHe said it was agreed "to wait and
OL,15,Fwatch over the coming days" regarding
OL,16,Ffuel prices and the government's
OL,17,Fresponse to the plight of farmers,
OL,18,Fsmall and medium enterprises, the
OL,19,Fhaulage industry, and other UK workers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776294181
OL,3,CPolice on alert as groups plan
OL,4,Cprotests over fuel prices across the UK
OL,6,F"There is huge concern that current
OL,7,Fpolicies are failing to address the
OL,8,Fpressures facing key sectors of the UK
OL,9,Feconomy," he said.
OL,11,F"It should be noted that Farmers For
OL,12,FAction was born out of the fuel strike
OL,13,Fof 2000, where the UK was brought to a
OL,14,Fstandstill for five days until
OL,15,Fgovernment listened - a lot was
OL,16,Flearnt."
OL,18,FDetails on exactly where protests
OL,19,Fcould be held remain fuzzy, but here
OL,20,Fis what police forces have said so far:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
