OL,3,CPolice on alert as groups plan
OL,4,Cprotests over fuel prices across the UK
OL,6,FPolice Scotland
OL,8,F"We are aware of potential planned
OL,9,Fprotest activity due to take place in
OL,10,Fvarious sections of the motorways in
OL,11,FScotland over the next few days,
OL,12,FWednesday 15 ` Friday, 17 April, 2026.
OL,14,F"We will have appropriate resources in
OL,15,Fplace to ensure the safety of those in
OL,16,Fattendance and mitigate disruption to
OL,17,Fthe wider community."
OL,19,FEssex Police
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
