PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776294181
OL,3,CPolice on alert as groups plan
OL,4,Cprotests over fuel prices across the UK
OL,6,F"We are aware of posts on social media
OL,7,Frelating to potential protest activity
OL,8,Fand we have plans in place to deal
OL,9,Fwith any disruption on our roads.
OL,11,F"Our priority is to keep Essex moving
OL,12,Fand we will deal robustly with anyone
OL,13,Fwho puts the safety of other road
OL,14,Fusers at risk."
OL,16,FKent Police
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
