FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776294181
OL,3,CPolice on alert as groups plan
OL,4,Cprotests over fuel prices across the UK
OL,6,F"We are aware of unsubstantiated posts
OL,7,Fon social media regarding the
OL,8,Fpotential for protests on the road
OL,9,Fnetwork nationally, but we have not
OL,10,Fbeen approached by anyone planning a
OL,11,Fprotest in Kent at this stage.
OL,13,F"Officers will continue to monitor the
OL,14,Fsituation."
OL,16,FSuffolk Police
OL,18,F"Police are aware of a potential
OL,19,Fprotest by farmers driving tractors in
OL,20,Fconvoy on the A14 to Felixstowe later
OL,21,Fthis week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
