PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776294181
OL,3,CPolice on alert as groups plan
OL,4,Cprotests over fuel prices across the UK
OL,6,F"If it does go ahead we will liaise
OL,7,Fwith the organisers to enable a
OL,8,Fpeaceful and safe protest but
OL,9,Fmotorists are advised there could be
OL,10,Fdelays on the A14."
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police
OL,14,F"A small protest is currently underway
OL,15,Fin Parliament Square. Officers are
OL,16,Fpresent and are in touch with
OL,17,Forganisers to ensure disruption is
OL,18,Fkept to a minimum."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
